            "chapterTitle": "Strict Orders for Observance of Obligatory Salat",
            "urn": 1621220,
            "body": "<p>Buraidah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"That which differentiates us from the disbelievers and hypocrites is our performance of Salat. He who abandons it, becomes a disbeliever.\"<br/><br/><b>[At-Tirmidhi]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
